<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 20:09:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普与以色列犹太至上主义者的邪恶联盟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/trumps-unholy-alliance-with-israels-jewish-supremacists/00000191-8f7f-d302-add5-9fff52da0000</link><description>下一届美国总统任期可能是以色列历史上影响最大的一届：以色列人和巴勒斯坦人再也负担不起特朗普给内塔尼亚胡的空白支票</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 18:09:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/trumps-unholy-alliance-with-israels-jewish-supremacists/00000191-8f7f-d302-add5-9fff52da0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党袭击未能引发全面战争后，美国看到了以色列与哈马斯谈判的前进方向</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/after-hezbollah-attack-failed-to-spark-all-out-war-u-s-sees-path-forward-for-gaza-talks/00000191-8f94-dd8c-addd-bff445990000</link><description>拜登政府官员认为，避免以色列与真主党发生广泛冲突会加剧辛瓦尔的孤立和谈判灵活性的压力。然而，关键问题，特别是以色列在加沙-埃及边境的存在仍未解决</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 17:30:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/after-hezbollah-attack-failed-to-spark-all-out-war-u-s-sees-path-forward-for-gaza-talks/00000191-8f94-dd8c-addd-bff445990000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方因计划放映有关以色列国防军在西岸活动的电影而关闭了阿拉伯犹太党总部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-shutter-arab-jewish-partys-hq-over-film-screening-on-idf-activity-in-jenin/00000191-8f89-dc4a-a59b-bfa94c900000</link><description>警方关闭了哈达什党的海法分部，原因是计划放映一部有关以色列军事活动的电影，他们声称该电影在以色列被禁止——而事实上，以色列法院已禁止放映同一导演于 2002 年创作的一部电影</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 17:19:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-shutter-arab-jewish-partys-hq-over-film-screening-on-idf-activity-in-jenin/00000191-8f89-dc4a-a59b-bfa94c900000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 325 天：以色列国防军下令撤离后，联合国在加沙的援助活动停止</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-325-un-aid-activity-in-gaza-halts-after-idf-evacuation-orders/00000191-8f97-d1d8-a9f9-9f972d620001</link><description>在开罗停战谈判中，埃及否认以色列声称其与加沙边境下的任何隧道都可用于走私的说法，重申不会接受以色列在费城走廊或拉法过境点的军事存在 ■ 警察部长本-格维尔声称有新的允许犹太人在圣殿山祈祷的政策 ■ 皇家约旦航空将从周二开始恢复飞往贝鲁特的航班 ■ 战争结束 325 天后，您需要了解以下信息</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 16:59:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-325-un-aid-activity-in-gaza-halts-after-idf-evacuation-orders/00000191-8f97-d1d8-a9f9-9f972d620001</guid></item><item><title>以色列著名歌手加入反对内塔尼亚胡政府举办的 10 月 7 日纪念活动的行列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/famed-singer-joins-mounting-opposition-to-netanyahu-government-run-oct-7-memorial/00000191-8eb4-dd8c-addd-bff40f070000</link><description>以色列演员兼歌手伊丹·阿梅迪作为以色列国防军预备役军人在加沙战斗中受重伤，他与其他名人和媒体人物一起反对利库德集团部长举行国营仪式的计划</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 14:12:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/famed-singer-joins-mounting-opposition-to-netanyahu-government-run-oct-7-memorial/00000191-8eb4-dd8c-addd-bff40f070000</guid></item><item><title>以色列南部女子被杀，警方因涉嫌谋杀逮捕丈夫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/bedouin-woman-killed-in-southern-israel-police-arrest-husband-on-suspicion-of-murder/00000191-8ed0-dc4a-a59b-bef8d9a70000</link><description>以色列警方逮捕了 27 岁受害者的丈夫，他的丈夫涉嫌用刀刺伤了她；今年以来共有145名阿拉伯裔以色列人被谋杀</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 14:01:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/bedouin-woman-killed-in-southern-israel-police-arrest-husband-on-suspicion-of-murder/00000191-8ed0-dc4a-a59b-bef8d9a70000</guid></item><item><title>资金枯竭，以色列初创公司纷纷倒闭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/its-directly-tied-to-the-war-money-has-dried-up-and-israeli-startups-are-folding/00000191-8e1a-dd8c-addd-bffea17e0000</link><description>去年，许多以色列科技公司关闭或大幅减少了活动。他们有一个共同点</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 12:45:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/its-directly-tied-to-the-war-money-has-dried-up-and-israeli-startups-are-folding/00000191-8e1a-dd8c-addd-bffea17e0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔是以色列新警察局长任命仪式上的真正明星</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-was-the-real-star-of-the-ceremony-to-appoint-israels-new-police-chief/00000191-8e3d-dc4a-a59b-bebdfde50000</link><description>丹尼·利维 (Danny Levy) 的任命已载入以色列历史：首次由一名已定罪的罪犯任命警察局长 ■ 警察的未来从未如此黑暗</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 12:07:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-was-the-real-star-of-the-ceremony-to-appoint-israels-new-police-chief/00000191-8e3d-dc4a-a59b-bebdfde50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院驳回反对没收反战抗议标语的请愿书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-dismisses-petition-against-confiscation-of-anti-war-protest-signs/00000191-8df3-d13a-ab93-ddf79c1d0000</link><description>高等法院法官表示，以色列警方的法律顾问已发布明确指示，反对没收标志，使得任何裁决都毫无意义</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 10:30:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-dismisses-petition-against-confiscation-of-anti-war-protest-signs/00000191-8df3-d13a-ab93-ddf79c1d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长取消晋升因对抗议者施暴而接受调查的警官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-voids-promotion-of-police-officer-investigated-for-violence-against-protesters/00000191-8d92-dab4-ad99-9db292f60000</link><description>上周，国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本·格维尔（Itamar Ben Gvir）非法提拔梅厄·苏伊萨（Meir Suissa）为总警司，警方消息人士称此举是卑鄙的机会主义，因为此举未经高级警务人员批准。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 09:33:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-voids-promotion-of-police-officer-investigated-for-violence-against-protesters/00000191-8d92-dab4-ad99-9db292f60000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔绘制了圣殿山/阿克萨大院的爆炸性愿景</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-charts-explosive-vision-for-temple-mount-al-aqsa-compound/00000191-8dab-d8bf-a7f9-9fffd4540000</link><description>经常访问该地点并呼吁违反现状的国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔在接受军队电台采访时表示，“恕我直言，我当选正是因为这个原因：确保圣殿山没有歧视性政策”</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 08:55:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-charts-explosive-vision-for-temple-mount-al-aqsa-compound/00000191-8dab-d8bf-a7f9-9fffd4540000</guid></item><item><title>与真主党的“反应方程式”让辛瓦尔和以色列陷入停火谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/question-of-response-to-hezbollah-attack-lets-sinwar-and-israel-delay-cease-fire-talks/00000191-8b62-dc4a-a59b-bbeaebce0000</link><description>真主党向辛瓦尔对以色列施加军事压力，为他争取时间来确定谈判节奏并坚持初步条件。内塔尼亚胡利用这段时间，就好像这也是他的日子一样，同时危及人质的生命</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 03:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/question-of-response-to-hezbollah-attack-lets-sinwar-and-israel-delay-cease-fire-talks/00000191-8b62-dc4a-a59b-bbeaebce0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称对约旦河西岸发动空袭，巴勒斯坦人报告五人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article-live/rocket-fired-at-tel-aviv-falls-in-nearby-suburb-palestinians-gaza-city-strikes-kill-five/00000191-8c67-d7f9-a5bd-be7777a50000</link><description>本-格维尔推动新的圣殿山政策；总理办公室：哈马斯呼吁西岸升级，现状不变 ■ 伊朗外长表示，德黑兰对以色列的反应将是“明确、经过深思熟虑且准确的” ■ 以色列国防军称，五个“空中目标”从黎巴嫩渗透到以色列，其中大部分被拦截</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 02:06:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article-live/rocket-fired-at-tel-aviv-falls-in-nearby-suburb-palestinians-gaza-city-strikes-kill-five/00000191-8c67-d7f9-a5bd-be7777a50000</guid></item><item><title>埃及否认以色列关于仍在使用的隧道仍然跨越加沙边境的说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/egypt-denies-israeli-claims-that-active-tunnels-still-run-across-border-with-gaza/00000191-8ab7-d8c0-abff-9aff5cb20000</link><description>埃及的这一说法不仅与内塔尼亚胡的评估相矛盾，而且与其他以色列高级官员对哈马斯在走廊活动的评估相矛盾</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 00:16:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/egypt-denies-israeli-claims-that-active-tunnels-still-run-across-border-with-gaza/00000191-8ab7-d8c0-abff-9aff5cb20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军命名在加沙中部战斗中丧生的以色列预备役士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-israeli-reserve-soldier-killed-in-central-gaza-combat/00000191-8b95-dd8c-addd-bbf556c40000</link><description>一名预备役军人也在导致来自阿什杜德的 36 岁军士长（预备役）什洛莫·叶霍纳坦·哈祖特 (Shlomo Yehonatan Hazut) 死亡的事件中受重伤。周日上午，以色列国防军宣布，来自杰瓦宾亚米的 21 岁中士戴维·摩西·本·希特里特 (David Moshe Ben Shitrit) 在真主党袭击以色列北部期间身亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 22:29:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-israeli-reserve-soldier-killed-in-central-gaza-combat/00000191-8b95-dd8c-addd-bbf556c40000</guid></item><item><title>今天以色列最重要的新闻与真主党无关</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-25/ty-article/.highlight/the-most-important-news-in-israel-today-had-nothing-to-do-with-hezbollah/00000191-89d8-dc4a-a59b-bbf86add0000</link><description>当我们在多个战线上与外部敌人作战时，以色列仍然因围绕国家民主基础的内部斗争而四分五裂，而这些基础正受到我们自己政府的攻击</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 19:49:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-25/ty-article/.highlight/the-most-important-news-in-israel-today-had-nothing-to-do-with-hezbollah/00000191-89d8-dc4a-a59b-bbf86add0000</guid></item><item><title>“他们只保卫特拉维夫”：以色列北方人在真主党袭击后感到愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/they-only-defend-tel-aviv-israeli-northerners-are-furious-after-hezbollah-attack/00000191-89e5-d31d-a3bf-8fff2c870000</link><description>在以色列先发制人的袭击和真主党对北部的火箭袭击之后，居民感到被遗弃和歧视。以色列北部三名议会主席宣布与政府断绝关系</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 19:33:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/they-only-defend-tel-aviv-israeli-northerners-are-furious-after-hezbollah-attack/00000191-89e5-d31d-a3bf-8fff2c870000</guid></item><item><title>《纽约时报》报道揭示了以色列对哈马斯辛瓦尔的“复杂且令人沮丧”的追捕行动的新细节</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/nyt-report-reveals-new-details-of-israels-complex-frustrating-pursuit-of-hamas-sinwar/00000191-8a2f-d13a-ab93-dabfd2c10000</link><description>《纽约时报》报道称，将辛瓦尔与奥萨马·本·拉登进行比较，寻找这位哈马斯领导人“更加复杂，甚至更加令人沮丧”，因为他继续领导哈马斯与以色列进行军事行动</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 18:40:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/nyt-report-reveals-new-details-of-israels-complex-frustrating-pursuit-of-hamas-sinwar/00000191-8a2f-d13a-ab93-dabfd2c10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列水手在真主党袭击以色列北部时丧生；以色列国防军探测船被击中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/israeli-sailor-killed-in-hezbollah-attack-on-northern-israel-idf-probing-ship-hit/00000191-8a4e-d13a-ab93-daff66d80000</link><description>陆军正在调查中士大卫·莫什·本·希特里特是否是被误击其船只的拦截火箭炸死，或者真主党无人机在该船上空被拦截后被弹片炸死</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 18:15:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/israeli-sailor-killed-in-hezbollah-attack-on-northern-israel-idf-probing-ship-hit/00000191-8a4e-d13a-ab93-daff66d80000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯媒体斥责真主党“鸡”袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/arab-media-raps-hezbollah-for-attack-that-didnt-spare-chickens/00000191-8a59-dc4a-a59b-baf91e4a0000</link><description>一位评论员谈到真主党对以色列上个月杀害一名真主党指挥官的反应时表示，“烈士们在目睹复仇的开始时感到高兴”，而真主党的反应只造成了轻微的损害。其他人则指出该组织期待已久的报复行动令人扫兴</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 18:14:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/arab-media-raps-hezbollah-for-attack-that-didnt-spare-chickens/00000191-8a59-dc4a-a59b-baf91e4a0000</guid></item></channel></rss>